sub_title: Human Resources Supervisor at The Hague Marriott
summary:
Last year student at the Hotel Management School Maastricht. Attend this education with a lot of ambition and perfection. Being friendly, social and service oriented with a strong drive.
Experienced the hospitality business through internships, work and education.
I'm highly motivated and enthusiastic to develop my talents in this field!

Words to describe me: hardworking, perfectionist, responsible, enthusiastic, eager to learn, social spontaneous
